result.adr_address: G/F, 36 Kweilin St, Sham Shui Po, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: G/F, 36 Kweilin St, Sham Shui Po, Hong Kong
result.name: GRIDDLE TOP

reviews.text:
Good food, best are the Teriyaki Chicken and Rice and the beef burger. Never need to wait for long

The portions are a little small though compared to the price. There are other places in the area that give more for less, but this is a nice place to visit every now and then
Yummy food!!! Didn't have to wait too long and was definitely worth the wait. Price wise isn't the cheapest you can find but is excellent. Perfect size for a feed

Like the food, but poooor customer service to foreigners. Orders are taken wrong quite often even I point to picture. Today, a skinny boy with glasses and hair in knot took my order. I pointed to picture of Tereyaki Chicken lunch and paid.  I return to my office and again the order is not what I ordered.  

This is the last time I eat the wrong food.

I called to tell them, and the person who answered the phone and spoke English OK until I explained  the problem and asked for now manager.  Then she said, sorry, I don't  speak English in perfectly good  english.  

She passed  the phone to another worker, and together they talked and laughed in background, while I said hello, hello...no answer.  Another person took the phone, said hello.  After I explained, she said sorry I don't speak English.  They each refused to give manager name. Finally, one person said manager name is Happy, but this could be wrong.  I will make a report with "Happy" in the next week.  

If you are a foreigner find another restaurant to eat at where you will be treated like respected customer.  These workers all represent the owner, company name very poorly.  

I will not eat here again.
Nice Japanese Fast Food featuring Teppanyaki Style Bento. Beef Cube is nice with Japanese Rice. But the side dish vegetable is poor

The bite size beef set doesn't worth the price they ask for--super Chewy beef bite which barely have taste of beef, along with overcooked corn and vegetable just won't cut....and how on earth one can make a PURE SOUR BUFFALO WINGS?! You can smell the sour favour from steps away FFS. 
Not a chance I'll make another visit...huge disappointment

result.name: 板上

reviews.text:
Good food, best are the Teriyaki Chicken and Rice and the beef burger. Never need to wait for long

The portions are a little small though compared to the price. There are other places in the area that give more for less, but this is a nice place to visit every now and then
六、七十元一個黑豚漢堡包🍔堂食還要用包裝紙包住上，靚極有限⋯⋯
方便排檔式、吃便檔的可來一嘗。
食物味道好，但坐位不太舒適，價錢中等，還可以接受，平少少更好

今次講下香港本土鐵板燒品牌-板上。😁 ⁣
⁣
黑豚漢堡。脆薯皇 （$62） ［好味度：7/10］⁣
一嚟就係見到一個超大嘅burger，成我手掌咁大呀。🖐️ 而且一咬落去佢係d汁係流曬出嚟。😚 我覺得佢嘅配料係做得仲好過主角豚肉㗎，因為佢嗰啲生菜番茄全部都好清新好fresh，同埋份量啱啱。🤩 好很正係個芝士，熔咗之後，勁重芝士味呀！😋 反而佢個肉呢就唔夠肉味，亦都係比較鞋啦，同埋肉汁都冇鎖好，分量都唔夠多，失色非常。😫 本身食完個包已經好飽，仲要送埋啲入面充滿好飽滿薯仔肉脆薯皇，真係飽上加飽，但係咁脆又唔捨得唔食。😅 ⁣
